            "title": "油價漲勢再現 道指曾挫逾300點",
            "description": "<p id=\"date\">2026年3月21日</p>\n<p class=\"info\">\t\n</p>\n    <h1 id=\"article-title\" class=\"sub_ex_article-title\">油價漲勢再現 道指曾挫逾300點<br>    \n   \n    </h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2026/03/21/4347280_847381c80fa780537d128fdb0aec412c.png\" title=\"\" class=\"thickbox\"><img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2026/03/21/4347280_847381c80fa780537d128fdb0aec412c_620.png\" border=\"0\"></a></p>\n<span class='enlargeImg'><a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2026/03/21/4347280_847381c80fa780537d128fdb0aec412c.png\" title=\"\" class=\"thickbox\"><img src='https://static.hkej.com/hkej/ejweb/enlarge.gif' align='absmiddle' />放大圖片</a> / <a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2026/03/21/4347280_847381c80fa780537d128fdb0aec412c.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">顯示原圖</a></span>\n<p></p>\n伊朗戰爭導致油價居高不下，引發全球各地央行加息的擔憂，美股周五早段繼續受壓，道指下跌超過300點。貨幣市場現時押注美國聯儲局今年10月底前有50%機會加息，交易員亦全面押注歐洲央行今年將加息3次。\n周五為美股「四期結算日」（Quadruple witching day），即指數及個別股份的期貨和期權...\n<p>（節錄）</p>",
